author: USA TODAY
title: Rosie Huntington-Whiteley, Jason Statham expecting their first child
text:
Rosie Huntington-Whiteley, Jason Statham expecting their first child Jayme Deerwester , USA TODAY 5:12 p.m. ET Feb. 9, 2017 14 Shares 
British model/actress Rosie Huntington-Whiteley and her action-star fianc√© Jason Statham just joined the impending celebrity parenthood club. 
Parenthood will be a very different action-adventure project for Rosie Huntington-Whitely and Jason Statham. (Photo: VALERIE MACON, AFP/Getty Images) 
Huntington-Whitely announced the news via a baby-bump-in-a-bikini-on-the-beach pic on Instagram post on Thursday, shot by the father-to-be. 
She wrote, "Very happy to share that Jason and I are expecting!" 
Huntington-Whitely, 29, and Statham, 49, dated for about five years before getting engaged in January 2016. She debuted her ring at that year's Golden Globes. 
Her post did not indicate when she's due or what gender the baby is. Regardless, the child will surely be blessed. A photo posted by Rosie Huntington-Whiteley (@rosiehw) on Feb 9, 2017 at 10:55am PST Read or Share this story: http://usat.ly/2k9hx6M Most Popular
